This project is build the recently popularized idea of training ivectors using ASR posteriors. 

Original paper:
Yun Lei; Scheffer, N.; Ferrer, L.; McLaren, M., "A novel scheme for speaker recognition using a phonetically-aware deep neural network," in Acoustics, Speech and Signal Processing (ICASSP), 2014 IEEE International Conference on , vol., no., pp.1695-1699, 4-9 May 2014


The main project is on the CRSS cluster. But the original repo was built on my local machine. 

Navid Shokouhi 
September 2015
